<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="PN216-intro">
      <p type="edition">tiṇaiyum tuṟaiyum avai. avaṉ vaṭakkiruntāṉpicirāntaiyārkku iṭaṉoḻukkaveṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p xml:lang="en" type="translation">  
      </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="PN216">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>kēṭṭaṉ māttirai yalla tiyāvatuṅ</l>
<l>kāṇṭa lillā tiyāṇṭupala kaḻiya</l>
<l>vaḻuviṉṟu paḻakiya kiḻamaiya rāyiṉu</l>
<l>maritē tōṉṟa lataṉpaṭa voḻukaleṉ</l>
<l>ṟaiyaṅ koḷḷaṉmi ṉāraṟi vāḷī</l>
<l>rikaḻvila ṉiṉiya ṉiyātta naṇpiṉaṉ</l>
<l>pukaḻkeṭa varūum poyvēṇ ṭalaṉē</l>
<l>taṉpeyar kiḷakkuṅ kālai yeṉpeyar</l>
<l>pētaic cōḻa ṉeṉṉuñ ciṟanta</l>
<l>kātaṟ kiḻamaiyu muṭaiya ṉataṉṟalai</l>
<l>yiṉṉatōr kālai nillala</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉē varukuva ṉoḻikkavavaṟ kiṭamē.</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l corresp="2">  “While many years have passed without seeing </l>
<l corresp="1">anything [of him] apart from hearing a bit, </l>
<l corresp="3">even though he is a lord who is familiar, without blemish, </l>
<l corresp="4">it would be difficult [for him] to turn up [here now]. ?????conduct”, </l>
<l corresp="5">don’t take up such doubt, you men of rare knowledge. </l>
<l corresp="6">He is without reproach, sweet, in friendship bound [to me]. </l>
<l corresp="7">He won’t want a lie that comes to get [his] fame lost. </l>
<l corresp="8">At the time his name rests, my name </l>
<l corresp="9a-c">says Pētai Cōḻaṉ. </l>
<l corresp="9d-10">He has a right to [my] exulted love. On top of that, </l>
<l corresp="11">at [this] time that is not pleasant he won’t stay [away]. </l>
<l corresp="12">He will come right now. May a place be kept for him. </l>
</lg>
    </div>
